item.title: Ike & Tina Turner - Proud Mary
item.description:
Proud Mary (Rolling on the River) by Tina Turner. It’s been lowered by 2 semitones to work with the diatonic set of color coded handbells / deskbells. For educational use.
If you found this video useful please subscribe. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
